data.description: Celebrate 2024 with this modern new home!  The open concept home has a great floor plan that features gorgeous, high-quality finishes throughout.  This home includes two master bedrooms with ensuites for a total of five bedrooms and four bathrooms.  The large kitchen has a huge amount of counter space and beautiful cabinetry.  The xeriscape front yard has a stunning waterfall feature, and the backyard is fully fenced. The deck has incredible mountain views and is perfect for entertaining. RV parking and electrical hookups are an added bonus.  Information provided as a courtesy, buyer and buyers agent to verify all.
